Q_{2 \times 3} \text{ is Quantity matrix then, what is the order}\\
\text{of the Price matrix P ?}

\text{If total Revenue matrix }
R = 
\left[\begin{array}{c}
r_1 \\ 
r_2 
\end{array} \right] = Q \times P \\
\text{where $r_1$ and $ r_2$ are the total revenues in}\\
\text{market I and market II respectively, then, is}\\
